(200, 'widget_raratheme_companion_faqs_widget', 'a:3:{i:1;a:3:{s:6:\"toggle\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"question\";a:4:{i:1;s:23:\"What is Rara Corporate?\";i:2;s:53:\"Can I use a RaraTheme theme on more than one website?\";i:3;s:61:\"It is a one time payment or do I have to purchase every year?\";i:4;s:28:\"Does RaraTheme offer refund?\";}s:6:\"answer\";a:4:{i:1;s:758:\"A corporation is a company or group of people authorized to act as a single entity (legally a person) and recognized as such in law. Early incorporated entities were established by charter (i.e. by an ad hoc act granted by a monarch or passed by a parliament or legislature). Most jurisdictions now allow the creation of new corporations through registration. Corporations enjoy limited liability for their investors, which can lead to losses being externalized from investors to the government or general public. Corporations are usually the most profitable and powerful business entities, such as their public control, influence over government (including political candidates that support them), and ability to protect its interests and make huge profits.\";i:2;s:255:\"Yes, you can use the theme on unlimited domains as all our themes are licensed under GPL license. You will get one theme license with the purchase.  You will also get free lifetime updates for the theme. Theme license is required to get the theme updates.\";i:3;s:201:\" Yes, it is a one time purchase. You pay only once and use the theme for the lifetime. You also get free theme updates for a lifetime. Plus, you get premium support for free for 12 months. No kidding. \";i:4;s:288:\"Yes, Rara Theme offers refunds to the customers within 15 days of the purchase. If the item(s) is broken, not working properly, or truly missing features from what is being mentioned on the sales page, we offer full refunds. Please refer to our terms and conditions for the refund policy.\";}}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;i:3;a:3:{s:6:\"toggle\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"question\";a:3:{i:1;s:52:\"Siapa yang akan mengerjakan proyek yang saya ajukan?\";i:2;s:78:\"Ke mana nantinya uang yang saya donasikan untuk proyek di Lailatul Coding ini?\";i:3;s:78:\"Bagaimana jika proyek yang saya ajukan tidak selesai di event Lailatul Coding?\";}s:6:\"answer\";a:3:{i:1;s:112:\"Nantinya, akan ada developer dan desainer yang secara sukarela mengerjakan proyek yang diajukan dalam 1 malam.\r\n\";i:2;s:286:\"Setiap uang yang didonasikan pada Lailatul Coding akan disalurkan kepada yang membutuhkan melalui Badan Amal yang menjadi partner kami. \r\nSebelumnya, dana donasi tersebut dapat disisihkan juga untuk tim developer jika mereka mau mengambilnya (maksimum 50%) dan 5% untuk panitia acara.\r\n\";i:3;s:328:\"Tim developer akan berusaha semaksimal mungkin untuk menyelesaikan setiap proyek yang ada dalam event Lailatul Coding. Pun jika ada proyek yang tidak selesai karena memang spesifikasi yang cukup sulit, bisa langsung dibicarakan antara Project Owner & tim developer untuk kesepakatan lebih lanjut di luar event Lailatul Coding.\r\n\";}}}', 'yes'),
